OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry, warm
OL,6,Fand mostly sunny evening. Remaining
OL,7,Fdry with clear spells overnight but
OL,8,Fbecoming chilly in the east with some
OL,9,Fpatchy mist and fog.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FAny early and low cloud mist
OL,12,Fin the east will quickly clear then a
OL,13,Fdry day with plenty of warm sunshine.
OL,14,FBecoming very warm again in the west.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA dry
OL,17,Ffew days with good spells of sunshine.
OL,18,FVery warm in the west with the best of
OL,19,Fthe sunshine, cloudier and cooler at
OL,20,Ftimes in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
